

{"id":6329,"date":"2024-03-14T13:29:34","date_gmt":"2024-03-14T06:29:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/?p=6329"},"modified":"2024-03-14T13:42:00","modified_gmt":"2024-03-14T06:42:00","slug":"4-cach-de-tap-luyen-khi-ban-qua-ban-ron","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/4-cach-tap-luyen-khi-ban-qua-ban-ron\/","title":{"rendered":"4 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n khi b\u1ea1n qu\u00e1 b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6330 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_7792-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_7792-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_7792-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_7792-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_7792-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_7792-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u00e3y tin r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch. T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3. V\u1eady l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd th\u1eddi gian m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd?<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">1. H\u00e3y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. S\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 45 ph\u00fat v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n trong tu\u1ea7n h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp v\u00e0i gi\u1edd m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n. Ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t th\u00f3i quen v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i t\u1eadp m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #009fc2;\"><b>2. T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">N\u1ebfu cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n, \u0111\u00f4i khi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i cu\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n, v\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 cu\u1ed9c g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi m\u1eddi sau gi\u1edd l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft, b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf b\u1ea1n! <\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">H\u00e3y l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng: b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd x\u1ea3y ra v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i. Sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n kh\u00e1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">3. T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n b\u00e8<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Khi g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n v\u00e0o l\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t c\u00f9ng nhau tham gia m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap c\u1ea3 hai t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u00f9ng nhau.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">4. \u0110i c\u1ea7u thang b\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c \u0111i d\u1ea1o trong gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 tr\u01b0a<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u1ecf kh\u00e1c trong th\u00f3i quen h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch. V\u00ed d\u1ee5, gi\u1eef d\u00e1ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111i l\u00ean c\u1ea7u thang thay v\u00ec \u0111i thang m\u00e1y. V\u00e0 thay v\u00ec ng\u1ed3i trong c\u0103n tin v\u00e0o gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 tr\u01b0a, h\u00e3y \u0111i d\u1ea1o. Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch Plank v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n th\u00ec sao? Plank m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat m\u1ed7i gi\u1edd gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1c c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f3. M\u1ed7i m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00fap \u00edch!<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u0110\u1ec3 vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u1edf n\u00ean hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, h\u00e3y l\u00e0m cho t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean trong l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap n\u00f3 h\u00f2a quy\u1ec7n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng thay v\u00ec tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian cho n\u00f3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The New Gym &#8211; Gym cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Email: cskh@thenewgym.vn<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Hotline: 1900 63 69 20<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Face